metadata.name: DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS
metadata.description:
You about to click on a link?

For some crazy too-good-to-be-true free mint you saw on a Twitter account you didn't know was hacked? Or because you missed out on Bored Apes? Or on Cryptopunks?  
Or whatever the latest thing is?

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

Or maybe someone's up in your DMs telling you they're gonna give you some Bitcoin?

They're not.

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

Or maybe human nature is kicking in and you're feelin' all hot and bothered? You wanna get your rocks off - from that supposedly hot thing tempting you in your DMs?

Stop.

And Remember...

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

This is your money.  
Your bank. Your treasury.  
Your Vault. To All your Art. 
Your Whole Collection.  
Your Self-Sovereignty.  
What you've worked hard for.

And there are unsavory types out there that want to take it ALL from you.  
A LOT of them.  
And they are relentless.

Is it worth it?

NO, IT'S NOT.

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

Slow down.  
Take a breath.  
It's gonna be alright.

Be mindful before you click on a link.

Or better yet...

Just

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

Inspired by the people coming together to help CryptoNovo when his wallet got hacked - no one is above it. It can happen to any of us.  
You can lose everything.

So, please...

DON'T CLICK ANY MOTHERFUCKING LINKS.

Produced by jonsey.  
Mixed and Mastered by Che Brooks.  
Written, Performed, Engineered and Arranged by Guido Corleone.  
Visual Art Created by Guido Corleone.
